      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been fully serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing play, providing the analog steering feedback these chassis are celebrated for. Finished in original paint with a flawless interior, this is a collector-quality example of the ultimate driving machine.",
