      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a limited-slip M-differential for optimal torque vectoring. Every bushing, damper, and cooling component remains in factory-fresh condition, offering the tactile steering feedback and mechanical harmony defined by the M-division's peak era. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
